Token.Abstract: The WonderPushDelegate protocol lets you customize various aspects of the WonderPush behavior at runtime.
Lets you overwrite URLs that WonderPush will open using UIApplication:openURL:.

Parameter.Name: URL
Parameter.Abstract: The URL that WonderPush is about to open.

ReturnValue.Abstract: A URL to open, or nil to avoid opening anything. Just return the value of the URL parameter to use the default WonderPush behavior.
